headline: Axon president talks tariff impacts & full-year outlook
summary: Axon (AXON) beat expectations on both revenue and earnings in the first quarter, and also raised its full-year outlook. Axon president Josh Isner joins Market Domination to explain what drove the beat and why the company felt confident raising its full-year forecast. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination here.
